title: 2 albums of Rajan Sajan Mishra
description:
Cassette rips in mono.

2 albums - 
Rajan Sajan Mishra - Ahead of Time, performing Raga Tilak Kamod

Rajan Sajan Mishra - A Marvel, 2 cassettes performing
Raga Miyan ki Malhar, Raga Surdasi Malhar, Raga Megh in first cassette and
Raga Malkauns, Tarana in Raga Kafi, Thumri in Raga Manj Khamaj and ending with a Chaiti in the second cassette.

192 KBps mp3s.
